title: Strange News: Putin's Secret Hideout, Nebraska and Ethanol, Buying the Lizzie Borden House
itunes:title: Strange News: Putin's Secret Hideout, Nebraska and Ethanol, Buying the Lizzie Borden House
description:
While detained by Russian authorities, opposition leader Alexei Navalny released a bombshell report on a secret, opulent compound allegedly owned in secret by Vladimir Putin. The Lizzie Borden house is officially for sale (as an AirBnB). And Mead, Nebraska struggles with largely unacknowledged, widespread contamination from a local ethanol plant. All this and more in this week's Strange News.
